<h2>Complete Visibility</h2>
<p>EDDI provides <strong>end-to-end observability</strong> across every conversation, pipeline step, and tool invocation. The immutable audit trail captures tokens used, latency, costs, and outcomes — enabling both operational monitoring and regulatory compliance.</p>

<h3>Observability Features</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Immutable Audit Trail</strong> — Cryptographically signed, tamper-evident operation logs</li>
<li><strong>Token & Cost Tracking</strong> — Per-conversation and per-agent usage metrics</li>
<li><strong>Pipeline Tracing</strong> — Full visibility into every step of the processing pipeline</li>
<li><strong>Prometheus Metrics</strong> — Standard metrics endpoint for monitoring infrastructure</li>
<li><strong>Grafana Dashboards</strong> — Pre-built dashboards for operations teams</li>
<li><strong>CQRS Telemetry</strong> — Event-sourced ledger of all system operations</li>
</ul>

</FeaturePage>
